longBusinessSummary: iMine Corporation does not have significant operations. It was previously engaged in the development and selling of computer equipments used for the mining of cryptocurrency. The company was formerly known as Diamante Minerals, Inc. and changed its name to iMine Corporation in March 2018. iMine Corporation was incorporated in 2010 and is based in Indianapolis, Indiana.
